      &lt;img alt="A photo of the Quest 3 and its controllers." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/mqgQVV3ZJ0_WyDky3RG4UhdJTpI=/0x3:4240x2830/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73449968/Quest3hero.0.jpg" /&gt;
