      &lt;img alt="Amazon Echo Spot smat speaker sitting on a table with cover art and title of a song “Electric Soul” playing via Amazon Music." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/02Nu-GLSyDjecNwmonS0aGWaffU=/200x0:2351x1434/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73449340/feature005_amazon_echo_spot_echo_spot_music_copy_2550x1434_1.0.jpg" /&gt;
